Police have released two surveillance videos that show a gunman just minutes before he shot dead three women and left another fighting for her life at a Florida hair salon.

The footage of Bradford Baumet, who turned the gun on himself after the shooting spree on Thursday, comes as police link the man to a fourth killing.

Baumet, 36, stormed the Las Dominicanas M & M Hair Salon in Casselberry at 11am shooting dead one customer and two salon employees.

