His estranged girlfriend and salon manager, Marcia Santiago, who was scheduled to appear in court for a domestic violence case against the man that day, was left severely wounded and remains in hospital. Baumet then shot himself dead at a friend's home nearby.

Newly obtained footage from security cameras at the Metro PCS store next door shows the gunman calmly walking to the salon and then running away less than a minute later, after the slayings.

